English: The children laughed and played under the afternoon sun.
Translation: Ang mga bata ay nagtawanan at naglaro sa ilalim ng hapon na araw.

English: She took a break to gather her thoughts.
Translation: Nagpahinga siya para mag-isip-isip.

English: The algorithm efficiently identifies patterns in large datasets.
Translation: Mabisang kinikilala ng algoritmo ang mga pattern sa malalaking dataset.

English: Data normalization helps improve model performance.
Translation: Tumutulong sa pagpabuti ng model ang normalisasyon ng datos

English: alam mo ma'am masaya naman topics natin sa philosophy inaantok lang talaga ko kasi ikaw nagdidiscuss
Translation: You know, ma'am, we have a lot of fun philosophy topics. I'm just really sleepy in what you're discussing.

English: It's raining cats and dogs.
Translation: Umuulan ng pusa at aso.

English: The party of the first part shall not be held liable for any unforeseen damages.
Translation: Ang partido ng unang bahagi ay hindi mananagot para sa anumang hindi inaasahang pinsala.

English: Thank you for coming to the event.
Translation: Salamat sa pagpunta sa kaganapan.

English: Despite her exhaustion, she finished the report before the deadline.
Translation: Sa kabila ng kanyang pagod, natapos niya ang ulat bago ang deadline.

English: That designer bag costs an arm and a leg.
Translation: Napakamahal ng designer bag na 'yan.

English: I didn’t want to go to the dentist, but I had to bite the bullet and get it over with.
Translation: Ayoko sanang pumunta sa dentista, pero kailangan kong tiisin ito para matapos na.

English: Mark accidentally let the cat out of the bag about the surprise trip.
Translation: Hindi sinasadyang nailabas ni Mark ang pusa mula sa maleta tungkol sa surprise trip.

English: I won’t be able to attend the meeting later because I’m feeling under the weather.
Translation: Hindi ako makakadalo sa meeting mamaya dahil masama ang pakiramdam ko.

English: Darkness is not heresy. It lies within us all.
Translation: Hindi kasalanan ang kadiliman. Nagsisinungaling ito sa loob natin.

English: This would be easier if blood came in more colours.
Translation: Ito ay magiging mas madali kung ang dugo ay dumating sa mas maraming kulay.

English: This guy right here is Shadow, and he's kinda my biggest rival. He's also a real buzz-kill.
Translation: Ang lalaking ito dito ay si Shadow, at siya ang aking pinakamalaking karibal. Isa rin siyang totoong buzz-kill.

English: Stealth is not your thing. But it's adorable you're willing to try.
Translation: Ang pagnanakaw ay hindi bagay sa iyo. Ngunit ito ay kaibig-ibig na handa kang subukan.

English: Cheddar cheese got its name from a village in what country?
Translation: Ang nayon na pinagkuhanan ng pangalan ng cheddar cheese ay nasaang bansa?

English: Which of the following tools is LEAST likely to be used in the process of creating a wood sculpture?
Translation: Alin sa mga sumusunod ang PINAKABIHIRANG ginagamit sa paggawa ng eskulturang kahoy?

English: With what would you use a "wah-wah pedal?
Translation: Ano ang gagamitin mo ng "wah-wah pedal?

English: Which of the following dental topics is developmentally appropriate for toddlers?
Translation: Alin sa mga sumusunod na paksa sa ngipin ang angkop sa pag-unlad para sa mga paslit?

English: The Bloons are back and better than ever! Get ready for a massive 3D tower defense game designed to give you hours and hours of the best strategy gaming available.
Translation: Ang Bloons ay bumalik at mas mahusay kaysa dati! Maghanda para sa isang napakalaking 3D tower defense na laro na idinisenyo upang bigyan ka ng mga oras at oras ng pinakamahusay na diskarte sa paglalaro na magagamit.

English: Sea of Thieves is a smash-hit pirate adventure game, offering the quintessential pirate experience of plundering lost treasures, intense battles, vanquishing sea monsters and more. Dive in with this revised edition of the game, which includes access to digital bonus media.
Translation: Ang Sea of Thieves ay isang smash-hit na pirate adventure game, na nag-aalok ng quintessential na karanasan sa pirata ng pagnanakaw sa mga nawawalang kayamanan, matinding labanan, pagtalo sa mga halimaw sa dagat at higit pa. Sumisid sa binagong edisyon ng larong ito, na kinabibilangan ng access sa digital bonus media.

English: The Binding of Isaac: Rebirth is a randomly generated action RPG shooter with heavy Rogue-like elements. Following Isaac on his journey players will find bizarre treasures that change Isaac's form giving him super human abilities and enabling him to fight off droves of mysterious creatures, discover secrets and fight his way to safety.
Translation: Ang The Binding of Isaac: Rebirth ay isang random na nabuong action RPG shooter na may mabibigat na elementong parang Rogue. Kasunod ni Isaac sa kanyang paglalakbay, ang mga manlalaro ay makakahanap ng mga kakaibang kayamanan na nagpabago sa anyo ni Isaac na nagbibigay sa kanya ng sobrang mga kakayahan ng tao at nagbibigay-daan sa kanya upang labanan ang napakaraming mga misteryosong nilalang, tumuklas ng mga lihim at labanan ang kanyang daan patungo sa kaligtasan.

English: Welcome to a new world! In Monster Hunter: World, the latest installment in the series, you can enjoy the ultimate hunting experience, using everything at your disposal to hunt monsters in a new world teeming with surprises and excitement.
Translation: Maligayang pagdating sa isang bagong mundo! Sa Monster Hunter: World, ang pinakabagong installment sa serye, masisiyahan ka sa pinakahuling karanasan sa pangangaso, gamit ang lahat ng iyong makakaya upang manghuli ng mga halimaw sa isang bagong mundo na puno ng mga sorpresa at kaguluhan.

English: For so long, you and me been finding each other for so long.
Translation: Matagal na, matagal na tayong dalawa naghahanap sa isa't isa.

English: I can't stop smiling when you're there
Translation: Hindi ko mapigilang ngumiti tuwing andiyan ka

English: I just want to be your everything.
Translation: Nais ko lang ay maging lahat para sa’yo

English: If I give you all my life, would you still be mine?
Translation: Kung ibibigay ko sa’yo ang buong buhay ko, akin ka pa rin ba?

English: A stack overflow happens when there is too much memory used on the call stack.
Translation: Nangyayari ang stack overflow kapag labis ang paggamit ng memorya sa call stack.

English: The database index speeds up data retrieval by reducing the number of disk accesses.
Translation: Pinapabilis ng database index ang pagkuha ng data sa pamamagitan ng pagbawas sa pag-access sa disk.

English: The kernel handles low-level operations in the operating system.
Translation: Pinangangasiwaan ng kernel ang mga low-level na operasyon sa operating system.

English: The address bus carries memory addresses to the CPU.
Translation: Dinadala ng address bus ang mga memory address papunta sa CPU.

English: Jollibee is a famous fast food restaurant in the Philippines.
Translation: Ang Jollibee ay isang sikat na kainan sa Pilipinas.

English: Filipinos visit their relatives during holidays.
Translation: Tuwing bakasyon, binibisita ng mga Pilipino ang kani-kanilang mga pamilya

English: Filipinos often use the expression "po" and "opo" as a sign of respect to elders.
Translation: Ginagamit ng mga Pilipino ang mga salitang “po” at “opo” bilang paggalang sa mga nakakatanda.

English: Adobo is one of the most popular dishes in the Philippines, made with soy sauce, vinegar, and garlic.
Translation: Ang Adobo ay isa sa mga pinakasikat na ulam sa Pilipinas at ito ay gawa sa toyo, suka, at bawang.

English: The hospitability of Filipinos are known worldwide
Translation: Ang pagiging hospitable ng mga Pilipino ay kilala sa buong mundo

English: We love to celebrate fiestas and gatherings with family and friends
Translation: Mahal natin ang pagdidiwang ng piyesta and salo-salo kasama ang pamilya at mga kaibigan

English: Adobo and sinigang are just some of the delicious Filipino dishes that are truly craved.
Translation: Ang adobo at sinigang ay ilan lamang sa masasarap na pagkaing Pilipino na talaga naman hinahanap-hanap

English: Eating rice with almost every meal is part of out culture
Translation: Bahagi ng ating kultura ang pagkain ng kanin sa halos bawat pagkain

English: The nurse inserted the IV incorrectly, causing bruising.
Translation: Ang nurse ay pinasok ang IV ng mali, kaya nagka-pasa.

English: The patient was given penicillin to prevent infection.
Translation: Ang pasyente ay binigyan ng penicillin upang maiwasan ang impeksyon.

English: To be able to start fasting, you have to stop eating and drinking anything except water at least 8 hours before your test.
Translation: Para makapagsimula ng fasting, tigilan ang pagkain at pag-inom 8 oras bago ang test, tubig lang pwede.

English: After being checked up, you have to be admitted to the hospital for observation and treatment.
Translation: Pagkatapos ng check-up, kailangang ma-admit ka sa ospital para ma-obserbahan at gamutan.

English: I always make it a priority to set aside time for my hobbies.
Translation: Lagi ko sinisigurado na maglaan ng oras para sa aking mga libangan.

English: One of the purposes of life is to help others without expecting anything in return.
Translation: Isa sa layunin ng buhay ay ang tumulong sa kapwa nang walang kapalit

English: I exclusively use Spotify to listen to music such as OPM.
Translation: Sa Spotify lang ako nakikinig ng music katulad ng OPM.

English: I have a large collection of non-fiction books that's always well-organized and clean.
Translation: Meron akong koleksyon ng mga non-fiction na libro na palagi ko sinisigurado na organisado at malinis.

English: Taking crazy things seriously is a serious waste of time.
Translation: Ang pagseseryoso ng mga bagay na baliw ay isang seryosong pag-aaksaya ng oras.

English: Things outside you are projections of what’s inside you, and what’s inside you is a projection of what’s outside.
Translation: Ang mga bagay sa labas mo ay salamin ng nasa loob mo, at ang nasa loob mo ay salamin ng nasa labas.

English: Some men are born mediocre, some men achieve mediocrity, and some men have mediocrity thrust upon them.
Translation: May ilang lalaking ipinanganak na katamtaman, may ilang nakakamit ang pagiging karaniwan, at may ilan na ipinipilit na lamang sa kanila ang pagiging ganoon.

English: Mother died today. Or maybe yesterday; I can't be sure.
Translation: Sumakabilang-buhay si Inay ngayong araw. O baka kahapon; medyo nalilito na ako.

English: The wave returns to the ocean, where it came from, and where it's supposed to be.
Translation: Bumabalik ang alon sa karagatan, kung saan ito nanggaling, at kung saan ito dapat nasa.

English: Sick of tea?! That's like being sick of breathing!
Translation: Ayaw mo na ng tsaa?! Parang sinabi mo na ring sawa ka nang huminga!

English: I wanted to invite my youngest to go get some ice cream, if he’ll let me.
Translation: Gusto ko imbitahin yung pinakabata kong anak para kumuha ng ice cream, kung papayagan niya ako.

English: That person has no more respect or love for you, leave them.
Translation: Wala nang respeto at pagmamahal yung tao para sa'yo, iwan mo na.
